    <p>When it comes to optimizing VPS servers for performance, InMotion knows what it takes. We do this by providing the having technical expertise, a speedy network, and multiple data center locations.</p>
    <h2>Technical Expertise</h2>
    <p>InMotion's technical support team is comprised of those who know hosting. From modifying server files, to helping our customers troubleshoot their installed platform such as Wordpress, Joomla, or Drupal. We monitor and offer advice to help you come up with a solution.</p>

    <h2>Speedy Network</h2>
